14
00:02:17.637 --> 00:02:19.737
after going into the woods despite a violent blizzard.

15
00:02:21.037 --> 00:02:25.137
After a while of searching for Mr. Nigaki in the woods,

16
00:02:25.137 --> 00:02:28.137
