24
00:02:54.937 --> 00:02:59.437
It's that person!

25
00:03:00.837 --> 00:03:06.637
"Bloody Valentine (Case Solved)"

26
00:03:12.837 --> 00:03:14.937
Now, all I need is the evidence.

27
00:03:14.937 --> 00:03:18.037
The evidence of the one who took the chocolate out of here.

28
00:03:18.037 --> 00:03:19.937
So long as I can get some evidence

29
00:03:19.937 --> 00:03:22.237
